NAME

    EMP_D_COMBAT - utility daemon for combat features

DESCRIPTION

    The combat daemon is a collection of combat-related helper functions.

    int hit_player(object hitter, object victim, int dmg, 
                   string dtype[, string weapon]) 

    int throw_player(object ply, int force[, string dir]):

    int stun_player(object victim, int dur[, object hitter]):

    int wound_player(object hitter, object victim, int dmg):

    void apply_liquid(object who, object liquid[, int clone_liquid]):

    int spray_liquid(object env, object liquid[, mixed exclude]):

    int spray_blood(object env, int val[, mixed exclude]):

